<subSubSection pageId="76" pageNumber="77" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="76.[151,1436,151,285]" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,152,176]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[322,430,152,176]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Igerna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sikkima">
<emphasis box="[322,430,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">I. sikkima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[576,771,152,176]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Igerna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="darjeelingensis">
<emphasis box="[576,585,153,176]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">I</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[600,771,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">darjeelingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but differs in the structure of the aedeagus. It lacks the apical processes present in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[426,621,188,212]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Igerna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="darjeelingensis">
<emphasis box="[426,621,188,212]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">I. darjeelingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but has a lamellate process at midlength of shaft. Both species occur in the same habitat and were swept from grassland mixed with herbs in 
<collectingRegion box="[935,1016,224,248]" country="India" name="Sikkim" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">Sikkim</collectingRegion>
along with specimens of 
<taxonomicName authority="C.A.Viraktamath, 2011" authorityName="C.A.Viraktamath" authorityYear="2011" box="[1307,1394,224,248]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Igerna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="keyae" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1307,1394,224,248]" italics="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">I. keyae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="76" pageNumber="77">
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="76" pageNumber="77" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
